msgid "header.subtitle"
msgstr "Please don't call sudden slack huddles without context"

msgid "header.introduction"
msgstr "Don't start a call without context. Provide context about what you need to discuss, how long it will take, and offer scheduling options. The person you're contacting might be in deep focus, in another meeting, or dealing with personal matters. It also might not be as much of a priority as you think."

