msgid "example.bad.body"
msgstr "**The issue:** Starting a call request without context forces the recipient to:\n\n- Stop their current work to decide if they want to talk\n- Mentally context-switch without preparation\n- Wonder if it's urgent or can wait\n- Feel obligated to respond immediately\n\nThis creates unnecessary interruptions and anxiety."

